<p>I am trying to redirect using web.config</p>  <p>if the url is <code>http://xyzsample.com</code> I want to redirect it to <code>http://www.xyzsample.com</code></p>  <p>I tried the below code</p>  <pre><code>&lt;rule name="Imported Rule 1-1" enabled="true" stopProcessing="true"&gt;                     &lt;match url="^(*.*)$" ignoreCase="true" /&gt;                     &lt;conditions logicalGrouping="MatchAll" trackAllCaptures="false"&gt;                         &lt;add input="{HTTP_HOST}" pattern="xyzsample.com" /&gt;                     &lt;/conditions&gt;                     &lt;action type="Redirect" url="http://www.xyzsample.com/{R:1}" redirectType="Permanent" /&gt;                 &lt;/rule&gt; </code></pre>  <p>But this is not redirecting and its causing <code>500 internal server error</code></p>